The '''Corbița Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Vrancea County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 25 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.sfin.ro/articol_13716/regele_asfaltului_toarna_si_un_parc_eolian.html Regele asfaltului toarna si un parc eolian {{ro}}] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716064348/http://www.sfin.ro/articol_13716/regele_asfaltului_toarna_si_un_parc_eolian.html |date=July 16, 2011 }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 50 MW of power, enough to power over 33,000 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$50 million.

