'''Plasma Surface Interaction''' (PSI) studies study the interaction at the interface between [[plasma (physics)|plasma]] and materials. Focus of the research lies on providing both theoretical and experimental support to the design and validation of [[plasma facing material]]s for the fusion experiment [[ITER]] and future devices.

